channel.description:
[center] [b]My super supporters! Mr extremez Fails arham 4 [/b] Temporarily using this banner. Just made it because I wanted to make the thread spunky ahaha! [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/I9nxl.png[/img] Hey! I am finally back and ready to work! I want to start a serious delta team. I haven't started yet but I already have the source downloaded and am now looking for a team. My main goal is to add unique content and make delta at its best! I am looking for developers that love delta and have experience, I am sick of PI's so I'm doing this. I am not going to host it from what I know now, unless the team wants to? Well if you want to get started and join the team apply please! [b]Server Developers: KroniKz_ Runescape Sucks Empty_ Empty_ Graphics Designer: KroniKz_[/b] How to Apply:
Name: Skype/MSN: Do you agree to being active on the weekends?(I don't mainly care about the weekdays, I have school too.) Years/months in programming?: Java only:
[b][u]My contact Info: Skype:roxofan17 MSN:PM me Facebook:PM me [/u][/b][/center]
Update Log: [b]-Started thread and started gathering team! 9.26.12 -Runescape Sucks joined the team 9,26,12 -Chose server to start with (delta++) 9.26.12[/b] -started doing some cleaning -KroniKz_ -9.27.12
